The paper deals with optimization problems related to the traveling salesman problem, which is a classic topic in computer science. The use of LP relaxation and integrality ratios suggests that the paper may belong to the sub-categories of Discrete Mathematics (cs.DM), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Computational Complexity (cs.CC), Graph Theory (cs.GT), or Robotics (cs.RO).
